{"tid":1231900,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"個人認為帶自己啲細蚊仔/女行入figure鋪但係又唔願買嘢俾細路果啲父母全部都係仆街嚟","createTime":"2019-06-16T13:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T09:06:58.000Z","uid":120980,"like":92,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"86faca764098ac7ec6d81174dc7cf0106b7788ee","tid":1231900,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"自己做開呢行 年中遇唔少呢啲閪父母<br />\n明知啲細蚊仔入到去鋪頭實會有嘢啱<br />\n明知啲細路見到啲啱嘅嘢實會扭計lur買嘢<br />\n<br />\n跟住當父母發覺啲細路睇啱玩具或者開聲求你買果陣<br />\n總係會彈出一句好例牌嘅戇鳩對白：嗱 ~ 齋睇唔買架<br />\n每次聽見呢句嘢我就心諗：屌你老母你唔想買就唔撚好帶啲細路入嚟俾啲假希望人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後咩情況相信大家都會估到 啲細路一哭二叫三典地<br />\n啲父母好啲嘅就齋秤翻個細路出去<br />\n衰啲嘢就直情拖出去打都見過<br />\n<br />\n真係搞成咁何必呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想買唔好帶啲細路入去咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105b7f2ea3bec3c97c54e5e3833c8b7eead7cc2e","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下下入去睇完都要買先害死個細路"},{"pid":"c1301ce0951ad54e23220a5c16e657abca4e64d7","tid":1231900,"uid":120980,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"105b7f2ea3bec3c97c54e5e3833c8b7eead7cc2e","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下下入去睇完都要買先害死個細路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n肯買就入<br />\n唔肯買就咪撚入<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n唔肯買又要入即係害死大家"},{"pid":"ddd8a14becd8357be78fa71b63f9ce08bc8e1e2f","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1301ce0951ad54e23220a5c16e657abca4e64d7","tid":1231900,"uid":120980,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"105b7f2ea3bec3c97c54e5e3833c8b7eead7cc2e","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下下入去睇完都要買先害死個細路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n肯買就入<br />\n唔肯買就咪撚入<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n唔肯買又要入即係害死大家"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"睇你咩角度啦 你做生意 賣家就當然想人幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買家就望清楚 格下價先啦<br />\n開得舖就預左俾人入俾人睇 <br />\n你唔想咪做網店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過仲麻煩仲多人運吉問長問短"},{"pid":"c1a86e87c12ee16b09e71fe16d18fee8b99e2730","tid":1231900,"uid":120980,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"ddd8a14becd8357be78fa71b63f9ce08bc8e1e2f","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1301ce0951ad54e23220a5c16e657abca4e64d7","tid":1231900,"uid":120980,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"105b7f2ea3bec3c97c54e5e3833c8b7eead7cc2e","tid":1231900,"uid":82398,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif